<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="logo-area">
    <view class="logo-badge">
      <van-icon name="shop-o" size="38" color="#274539" />
    </view>
    <view class="app-name">简家厨</view>
    <view class="slogan">一道菜，让大人和宝宝都吃得更安心</view>
  </view>

  <view class="login-panel" wx:if="{{!loggedIn}}">
    <view class="panel-copy">
      <text class="panel-kicker">ACCOUNT ACCESS</text>
      <text class="panel-title">登录后同步会员、收藏与采购清单</text>
      <text class="panel-desc">保留偏好设置，在小程序与 App 间获得一致体验。</text>
    </view>

    <button 
      class="btn-wechat" 
      bindtap="wechatLogin" 
      loading="{{loading}}"
    >
      {{loading ? '登录中...' : '微信一键登录'}}
    </button>
    
    <view class="divider">
      <view class="line"></view>
      <text class="text">或</text>
      <view class="line"></view>
    </view>
    
    <button 
      class="btn-guest" 
      bindtap="guestLogin"
      loading="{{loading}}"
    >
      游客体验
    </button>
    
    <view class="tips">
      登录后可使用收藏菜谱、生成购物清单、家庭共享等完整能力。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="user-panel" wx:else>
    <view class="avatar-shell">
      <van-icon name="user-o" size="34" color="#274539" />
    </view>
    <view class="username">{{userInfo.username || '用户'}}</view>
    <view class="role">已登录</view>
    <view class="status-note">你的偏好与权益已准备就绪，可继续浏览推荐或同步到其他设备。</view>
    
    <button class="btn-logout" bindtap="logout">退出登录</button>
  </view>
</view>
